possible development of tuberculosis in patients who tested negative for latent tuberculosis infection prior to initiating therapy.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/124511/', '[1] "Product Information. Xeljanz (tofacitinib)." Pfizer U.S. Pharmaceuticals Group, New York, NY.', 'Apremilast, Pirfenidone, Belumosudil, Teprotumumab, Ravulizumab, Pegcetacoplan, Eculizumab, Sutimlimab', NULL, 1767369485);
